{
  "texts": [
    "This biological conduction forms the foundation of our taste perception.",
    "Similarly, electronic tongues utilize sensor arrays to detect and analyze taste molecules through sophisticated signal transmission, mimicking the biological process.",
    "Artificial intelligence is significantly reshaping the landscape of gustatory research by providing advanced methodologies for flavor analysis and taste prediction.",
    "Researchers can leverage powerful AI techniques to interpret the complex data generated from both biological and electronic systems.",
    "This approach facilitates deeper insights into gustatory mechanisms and enhances our understanding of flavor perception, ultimately influencing consumer preferences and product development."
  ]
}